		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64482111"><p>The cloud is what saved them. They had an off-site backup at a different cloud provider.</p><p>If they were working out of an on-premises data center and it failed, they still would have needed an off-site backup to restore from.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64482111">

